So just because human
beings are uniquely

00:24:11.800 --> 00:24:14.770
able to engage in
Mental Time Travel,

00:24:14.770 --> 00:24:18.040
doesn't mean we're actually
particularly good at it.

00:24:18.040 --> 00:24:23.290
And so learning to
delay gratification

00:24:23.290 --> 00:24:27.790
and learning to withhold
immediate rewards for longer

00:24:27.790 --> 00:24:31.120
term benefits is something our
species is uniquely able to do,

00:24:31.120 --> 00:24:32.960
but it's also something
we struggle with.

